To Embed Sorting in Search Result:
<@liferay_portlet["runtime"]
  instanceId="Unique-ID"
  portletName="com_liferay_portal_search_web_internal_sort_portlet_SortPortlet_INSTANCE_nndp_sortSelection"
/>

To Embed Commerce product category navigation:
<@liferay_portlet["runtime"]
  portletProviderAction=portletProviderAction.EDIT
  instanceId="Unique-ID"
  portletName="com_liferay_commerce_product_asset_categories_navigation_web_internal_portlet_CPAssetCategoriesNavigationPortlet"
/>
